name: SUNKEN (itch) (Teams24)
description:
Aliens have attacked earth the only place safe is in underwater and the antimatter railguns strategically placed. Underwater railguns are the last line defense against aliens and last hope for humanity 

The only way to transport the ammunition is to go underwater and and cant use torpedos as aliens are immune to traditional explosion  based arms

Deliver the animatter warheads to each loading station of the railguns
